Package: networkR
Title: Flexible Bayesian Network Pipelines for Experimental Studies
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: NetworkR Authors
Maintainer: NetworkR Authors <packages@example.com>
Description: Provides a configurable pipeline for Bayesian network structure
    learning in factorial and repeated-measures studies. The package supports
    panel ingestion, derived design variables, predictive mean matching
    imputation, Hartemink discretization, blacklist construction, bootstrap
    stability estimation, structure comparison, and ggraph-based network
    visualization.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://gwmcelfresh.github.io/networkR/
BugReports: https://github.com/GWMcElfresh/networkR/issues
